&lt;p&gt;Our API still works, but obviously our &lt;code&gt;DBAccessModule&lt;/code&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;code&gt;DAOModule&lt;/code&gt; are still unused. Let&amp;#39;s address that. &lt;/p&gt;
